{"tid":1940352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角2人違反隔離令 警員到場助保護衣員帶往駿洋邨","createTime":"2020-03-23T17:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T17:10:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b59d3c9c083de7f72fa216c32d6dd3c64ab0e9e","tid":1940352,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"旺角2人違反隔離令 警員到場助帶往駿洋邨<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上9時許接獲醫療輔助隊人員報案，指在旺角西洋菜南街152號一個單位執行職務期間，遇到2人涉嫌違返隔離令，拒絕被移送往駿洋邨的強制檢疫隔離中心。警方及<span style=\"color: gold;\">衛生署人員</span>到場，<span style=\"color: gold;\">由身穿保護衣的人員上樓</span>，其後將1名女子及1名小童帶上車，送往駿洋邨進行強制隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275910&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275910%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1oGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=241e9132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275910&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}